---
title: Dukkah Cauliflower & Pearl Couscous Salad with Roasted Veggies & Garlic Yoghurt
description: This delightful dish is a celebration of wholesome roasted veggies with pearl couscous and fragrant mint. Add dukkah and roasted almonds for extra flavour and crunch, then top it off with a drizzle of garlicky yoghurt.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ec6342d81d3ba5450034e74-7691f000.jpg
